## 📄 **الملف 5: .gitignore**

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
env/
venv/
ENV/
env.bak/
venv.bak/

# Database
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Logs
*.log
*.log.*

# Termux
/data/data/com.termux/
/storage/

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-*

# Local
.env
.config
.cache
.local
